Simple OS:

To build:
export K1_TOOLCHAIN_DIR=<toolchain>
make

To run on hardware:
make hw_jtag_test 

To run on simulator:
make sim_test

Simple OS is a multi-processor, multi-thread OS, preemptive OS. Its source code can be found in os/.
A simple test that spawns 16 processors in a single cluster and creates 16 threads on each processor can be found in test/.

Simple OS relies on the Kalray hypervisor and vbsp library. 